creator: D&K Group
descriptionHtml:
Alpesh Jhaveri , the founder of Aman Gem, solely started this company from scratch in 1999.
He is renowned in the diamond market for his unparalleled work ethics and the principles.
Back in time Aman Gem was known as Clean Diamonds,a Family business where they took on the risk and reward of creating something from nothing.
Energetic and imperious,astute and smooth,modest and zealous are some adjectives describing the years of hard work done by Alpesh Jhaveri to build the company.
He is renowned in the diamond market for his unparalleled work ethic and the principles.
THE ONLY BROWNS COLLECTION MAKES ITS DEBUT, HERALDING A NEW ERA WITH IT.
CAPTURING THE LOVE, ELEGANCE, CHEERFULNESS, STRENGTH, AND CREATIVITY THAT ONLY BROWNS STANDS FOR, THIS COLLECTION QUICKLY BECOMES AN ICON FOR THE AGES.
WE HAVE LAUNCHED OUR NEW WEBSITE AND MOBILE APPLICATION (SPECIFICALLY FOR BIG SIZES OF BROWN DIAMONDS - 2 CARATS TO 10 CARATS)
App Features Include:
- Manage your online account with AmanGem
- Search diamonds by different parameter criteria
- View real images of diamonds
- View and verify grading certificate of diamonds
- Save you searches
- Manage your online cart
- Track your selected diamonds
So what are you waiting for? Download AmanGem app now and request for online account to explore your desire diamonds online.
